14:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Soliq peniyalari kalkulyatori O'zbekistonda soliqlarni o'z vaqtida to'lamaganligi uchun penya miqdorini hisoblaydi. Penya avtomatik ravishda Markaziy bankning qayta moliyalash stavkasining 1/300 qismi miqdorida har bir kechiktirilgan kun uchun hisoblanadi. Joriy MB stavkasi 14% da bu 14%/300 = 0,047%/kun (yillik 17,0%) ni tashkil etadi. Penya belgilangan to'lov muddatidan keyingi birinchi kundan boshlab haqiqiy to'lov kunigacha hisoblanadi. Kalkulyator sizning ma'lumotlaringiz bo'yicha aniq penya summasini aniqlaydi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash formulasi: Penya = Qarz summasi × (MB stavkasi / 300) × Kechikish kunlari soni. MB stavkasi 14% da: kunlik stavka = 14%/300 = 0,0467%. Misol: "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/jshshs","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"JShShS"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" bo'yicha 5 000 000 so'm qarzdorlik, 60 kun kechikish. Penya = 5 000 000 × 0,000467 × 60 = 140 000 so'm. Katta summalarda penya tez yig'iladi: 100 mln so'm qarzdorlikda oylik penya taxminan 1 400 000 so'm, yillik — taxminan 17 000 000 so'm."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Penyadan tashqari, soliq huquqbuzarliklari uchun jarimalar nazarda tutilgan. Soliq deklaratsiyasini kechiktirganlik uchun (2026-yildan): jismoniy shaxslar va YaTTlar uchun 1 "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/bhm","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"BHK"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" (412 000 so'm), yuridik shaxslarning mansabdor shaxslari uchun 3 BHK. Soliq bazasini kamaytirganligi uchun: kam to'langan soliq summasining 20%. Ro'yxatdan o'tmasdan faoliyat yuritganligi uchun: olingan daromadning 10%, lekin kamida 1 mln so'm (SK 219-moddasi). Soliq organining so'rovi bo'yicha hujjatlarni taqdim etmaganligi uchun: 5 BHK."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Soliq kodeksi muayyan hollarda penyani hisobdan chiqarish imkoniyatini nazarda tutadi. Agar soliq to'lovchi soliq tekshiruvigacha xatoni mustaqil aniqlagan va aniqlashtirilgan deklaratsiya topshirgan bo'lsa, bazani kamaytirganlik uchun jarima qo'llanilmaydi (lekin penya baribir hisoblanadi). Qarzdorlikni qayta tuzilashda penya bo'lib to'lash mumkin. Soliq nizolari yuqori turuvchi soliq organi orqali ma'muriy tartibda yoki sud orqali ko'rib chiqiladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],"$L19"]}]]}],"$L1a","$L1b","$L1c"]}]
